crew of space shuttle discovery times edt 
537 am crew awakens exercises and has breakfast 
637 am photograph lightning in the atmosphere 
708 am turn on furnace for materials processing experiments 
842 am activate experiment on growing crystaline films 
1042 am test affect of weightlessness on the viscosity of 
red blood cells 
1237 pm meal followed by experiment continuation and 
monitoring spacecraft systems 
637 pm meal 
837 pm start 8hour sleep period 
