weightlessness hilmers explained it could have medical 
applications such as separating malignant from nonmalignant cells 
in earths gravity when materials like the astronauts are 
testing are mixed the lighter one tends to float to the top 
hilmers said in zero gravity its more like a yoke floating 
inside the egg white 
one of the things this can show said hilmers is the use 
of people in space to look at experiments and see any changes we 
