of the central committee to go along with his politburo status 
alexandra p biryukova the highestranking woman in the soviet 
hierarchy gained an alternate or nonvoting politburo spot as 
did anatoly i lukyanov and interior minister alexander v vlasov 
the nations top policeman 
ms biryukova who was responsible for the consumer sector 
becomes the first woman named to the politburo since culture 
minister yekaterina furtseva was a full voting member from 1957 to 
1961 under nikita s khrushchev 
