nigeria and the philippines 
the group visited cuba sept 1626 on a mandate from the 
commission which last march accepted an invitation from castro to 
visit the island and investigate the human rights situation 
the invitation followed a twoyear effort by the united states 
to have cuba put on the commissions agenda 
