unsuccessful negotiations between the union and caterpillar 
worlds largest manufacturer of earthmoving equipment and the 
union 
the decision to extend the negotiations puts on hold strike 
plans by the companys bluecollar workforce in factories in 12 
cities in illinois iowa pennsylvania colorado and tennessee 
